{"id":4141,"date":"2025-06-16T13:32:17","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:32:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4141"},"modified":"2025-06-16T13:32:17","modified_gmt":"2025-06-16T06:32:17","slug":"hang-rao-bao-ve-da","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/hang-rao-bao-ve-da\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da &#8211; L\u1edbp l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn quan tr\u1ecdng cho l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, l\u00e0n da ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m. Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u00e2m th\u1ea7m l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, khi\u1ebfn da tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u1ed1n c\u00f3. V\u1eady h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe \u0111\u1eb9p? V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u201cl\u00e1 ch\u1eafn\u201d t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u00e0y? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hang-rao-bao-ve-da-va-chuc-nang-quan-trong\"><\/span><b>H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng quan tr\u1ecdng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 l\u1edbp s\u1eebng bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec, l\u00e0 l\u1edbp ngo\u00e0i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a da, g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 bao ph\u1ee7 b\u1edfi l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng lipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u201ct\u1ea5m khi\u00ean\u201d gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u1ee7a da v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc qua da, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi vi khu\u1ea9n, vi n\u1ea5m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4142\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4142\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4142\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-1.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4142\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, da s\u1ebd duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebb m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u00f3i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t, da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, n\u1ed5i m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf hay g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia trong ng\u00e0nh da li\u1ec5u, vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng xung quanh. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef g\u00ecn v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhung-yeu-to-lam-suy-yeu-hang-rao-bao-ve-da\"><\/span><b>Nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef g\u00ecn l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f3i quen v\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu n\u00f3. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4143\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4143\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4143\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-2.webp\" alt=\"Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4143\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i l\u1edbp d\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean tr\u00ean da, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 suy gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Khi \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec, da d\u1ec5 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da sai c\u00e1ch: H\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y, da ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc, khi\u1ebfn vi khu\u1ea9n t\u00edch t\u1ee5 v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u2014 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 gia t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 vi\u00eam da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c: Khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u00e3o h\u00f3a, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i. L\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ecfng h\u01a1n, l\u00e0m da d\u1ec5 kh\u00f4, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 suy y\u1ebfu ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 stress oxy h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV: Tia UV t\u1eeb m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da, v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 n\u00e1m v\u00e0 t\u00e0n nhang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng: M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da suy y\u1ebfu, l\u00e0m da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-the-nao-de-biet-hang-rao-bao-ve-da-bi-ton-thuong\"><\/span><b>L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o n\u00e0y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac bi\u1ec3u m\u00f4 c\u1ee7a da \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng sinh l\u00fd di\u1ec5n ra b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u00fap da duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba s\u1ef1 x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp c\u1ee7a vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hang-rao-bao-ve-da-khoe-manh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi nhau, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp ch\u1eafn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn. Da lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o (t\u0103ng s\u1eebng, r\u1ee5ng s\u1eebng) di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n s\u0103n ch\u1eafc, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 \u00edt b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hang-rao-bao-ve-da-bi-ton-thuong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu, c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ea5t k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ebf b\u00e0o: C\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o s\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd. T\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c khe h\u1edf v\u1eadt l\u00fd. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: Nh\u1eefng khe h\u1edf n\u00e0y l\u00e0m n\u01b0\u1edbc trong da tho\u00e1t ra ngo\u00e0i. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u00e0 lipid c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho da. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4, thi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng sinh l\u00fd da: Khi \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 lipid kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec, pH c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp axit mantle thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 vi sinh v\u1eadt tr\u00ean da. Vi khu\u1ea9n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 l\u00e0m r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n h\u1ec7 mi\u1ec5n d\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a da. G\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng vi\u00eam kh\u00f3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuc-hoi-hang-rao-bao-ve-da-tu-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, li\u1ec7u n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t ra khi ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 da c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i trong m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng x\u1ea3y ra. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da m\u00e0 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4146\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4146\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4146\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-3.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4146\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"giu-am-va-duy-tri-do-am-cho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u1eef \u1ea9m v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m, vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 pH c\u1ee7a da. \u0110\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, pH da n\u00ean duy tr\u00ec trong kho\u1ea3ng 5.5 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh axit nh\u1eb9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4031\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4031\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4031\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp\" alt=\"D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/37-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4031\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH qu\u00e1 cao ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5p s\u1ebd l\u00e0m h\u1ecfng l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, khi ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch, h\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1eeb 4.0 &#8211; 5.0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"duong-am-voi-cac-thanh-phan-hieu-qua\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m cho da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1edbp s\u1eebng v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 Ceramides, Glycerin, Hyaluronic Acid (HA), Vitamin E (Tocopherol), Niacinamide (Vitamin B3) v\u00e0 Panthenol (Vitamin B5) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u khuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tranh-lam-dung-cac-san-pham-co-thanh-phan-hoat-tinh-manh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u00e1nh l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 axit AHA, BHA hay c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho da khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4147\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4147\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4147\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-4.webp\" alt=\"Tr\u00e1nh l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4147\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tr\u00e1nh l\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb kh\u00f4, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Eczema hay Rosacea. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 ho\u1eb7c chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-kem-chong-nang-moi-ngay\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm t\u1eeb \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. Khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, collagen trong da b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ee7y, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m da l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed gia t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc ung th\u01b0 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3901\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3901\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3901\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/31-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3901\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1eady l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y? Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng <\/span><b>kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean. C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da s\u1edbm nh\u1edd v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe l\u00e0n da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n gi\u00e0u axit b\u00e9o thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c b\u1ed5 sung th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hang-rao-bao-ve-da-bao-lau-phuc-hoi\"><\/span><b>H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da bao l\u00e2u ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh dung, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ed1c th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4148\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4148\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4148\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-5.webp\" alt=\"H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/62-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4148\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ol>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh: N\u1ebfu h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1eb9, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn 1 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp s\u1eebng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da y\u1ebfu: Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p da \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 da kh\u00f4, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1edbp b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da v\u00e0 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3m m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, da tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u00edt nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam s\u01b0ng, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, v\u00e0 da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u1ea7n h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da m\u00e0 c\u00f2n mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. C\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 chi ti\u1ebft, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. T\u00ednh uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1eeb GSC c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da l\u00e0 g\u00ec? V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u201cl\u00e1 ch\u1eafn\u201d t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u00e0y? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4149,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4141","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4141","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4141"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4141\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4150,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4141\/revisions\/4150"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4149"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4141"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4141"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4141"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}